title: A1466 - 820-00165-A no boot 40ma
message:
Hello,

We have a Macbook Air not powering on. 
Draws 40ma

We have PP3v3S5 but no S4 rails
S4 Power Enable is missing 

PM SLP S5 L is 0v
SMC_S4_WAKESRC_EN 0v

PP3V42_G3H 3.44v
SMC RESET L 3.4v

Is this SMC issue?

SMC is not hot.
